<p>Little Hanoi Restaurant<br />
 147, Curtain Rd, London, EC2A 3QE</p>

<p>Our comment: A little Gem of a place. Great spicy stock with
good fresh ingredients. Looked a bit commercial, non-authentic from
the outside, but the Bo Bun Hue we had was among the best we've
had.</p>

<p>Tragically the picture of the food has been lost from my camera
phone.</p>
